commentable_entity.title: 20th Century Fox: Justice for Johnny Depp
commentable_entity.description: So I am creating a petition to serve justice for Johnny Depp. Recently he lost a liability case with Britain’s New Sun. He has been going through a lot this year not only that, but he has also been through a court case with his ex-wife Amber heard. There is already a petition online to get her removed from Aquaman 2. There is also another petition online to get Johnny Depp hired back on to the set of fantastic beasts and where to find them 3. I highly encourage all of you to sign both of those petitions, and I highly encourage all of you to sign this one, as well. Johnny Depp is one of the most selfless, loving, caring, kind hearted, gentle souls in the world. He has made some mistakes in the past, but we all have. His ex-wife Amber heard has also falsely accused him of beating her, and in reality, she is the one who put her hands on him. I personally believe that also Warner Brother Studios isn’t being fair to him, at all. He has gotten more crap this year than most people have. So like I said, I highly encourage all of you to please sign the two previous petitions I listed above. And I highly encourage you to please sign this one. This man deserves all of our love, and he deserves all of our support. Justice for Johnny Depp. Johnny Depp has helped more people than we can even begin to imagine or count. Now, it’s time for us all to stand together as one, and to finally help him.
